      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MADE IN LONDON (1) slowly into stride off the rails but wound up into the minor place when a 4.5 lengths second (17.59) at this track in Grade 5. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Rates highly and will give a great sight. OKEY (2) missed the hat-trick last start when fifth and beaten 8 lengths (17.85) last time at this track. Solid record at this trip including 23 wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. TINKER AMINA (4) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 17.62 beating Bedazzled Jewel. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. One of main contenders. RIPPED RACCOON (6) recorded a 10 length win (17.18) in a Mix 2/3 last time at this track. Has an unbeaten record from this draw, scoring two times.",
